room_title: Escape room "Studio Wonderland" by Escape It Houston in Houston
review: Room was incredibly well made. Loved the puzzles. It was a bit warm and the game master spoke way too quickly. But over all it was a great experience and would love to be back again.

room_title: Escape room "Studio Wonderland" by Escape It Houston in Houston
review: Awesome.!!!! establishment staff is very professional the manager Kellie.!! Is beautiful she has the type of  personality that caters to all customers. This is a must do if you are in the Humble area in Houston Texas.!!!

room_title: Escape room "Studio Wonderland" by Escape It Houston in Houston
review: Great Room.  Feels like a miniature 70s disco.  The props included a lighted dance floor, turn tables, and bottles.  It was neat when we unlocked a certain clue the entire dance floor and lights come to life, and music started playing.  Some of our group dressed up in our club clothes to play this one.   A lot of fun, recommend!
